notes:
Much better works with disabling ESYNC. If you want play with native resolution, you must edit registry key (this problem in windows too):
1) protontricks 254060 regedit;
2) Go to HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Reality Pump\KnightShift\BaseGame\Graphics\Setup and edit string "ShowAllRefreshRates" from 0 to 1;
3) Check your resolution in game.
